    UC23
    UC24
}

package "Notification System" {
    UC29
    UC30
    UC31
    UC32
    UC33
}

' Detailed Flow Notes
note right of UC1
  Invitation Process:
  - Select user role and permissions
  - Generate secure invitation link
  - Send email with invitation
  - Track invitation status
  - Set expiration date
end note

note right of UC15
  Mention System:
  - @username mentions
  - Role-based mentions (@team, @managers)
  - Project-wide mentions
  - Email notifications for mentions
  - Mention history tracking
end note

note left of UC22
  Version Control:
  - Automatic version tracking
  - Compare file versions
  - Restore previous versions
  - Version comments and tags
  - Branching support
end note

note bottom of UC25
  Activity Feed:
  - Real-time updates
  - Filter by user/project
  - Activity categories
  - Timestamp tracking
  - Export activity logs
end note

' Exception Handling
note top of UC5
  Invitation Revocation:
  - Immediate access removal
  - Notification to invitee
  - Reason for revocation
  - Audit trail creation
  - Cannot be undone
end note

' Actor Generalizations
TM <|-- PM
External <|-- TM

' Security and Compliance Notes
note right of UC37
  Access Audit:
  - Log all permission changes
  - Track role assignments
  - Monitor access patterns
  - Generate compliance reports
  - Alert on suspicious activity
end note

@enduml
